bDIModel

Class Agent

  • java.lang.Object
    • bDIModel.Agent

  • public class Agent
extends java.lang.Object
    The Agent class objects have a ArrayList of Belief, Plan, Goal, Event and Import of the Agent. The set and get methods are used to set and get the elements of each ArrayList.
    Author:
    NandaKumar Derek Moayad
